{"tid":2046653,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"話你知點樣喺唔違法嘅情況下，用美元取代港元！","createTime":"2020-06-01T14:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T14:20:33.000Z","uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e81ddeecb020ae4b37593ab0c220717658870c3","tid":2046653,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:13:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>十一月推呢個 idea 嘅時候氣候未適合冇乜人睇<br />\n而家講多次唔知大家點諗？<br />\n以下係我當日提出嘅諗法：<br />\n<br />\n</strong><br />\n之前叫大家開始唱美金。但係老實講，成效唔大，真係唱嘅人有幾多？<br />\n<br />\n其實唱美金嘅困難喺邊度？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係用唔到，唱完只可以擺床下底呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁點解決？好簡單。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你俾我用，我咪唱多啲囉。<br />\n如果黃色經濟圈開始接受美金付款，我真係唔介意唱多啲。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但係，而家根據法例商店必須接受港元作為付款選項。咁點更上一層樓，鼓勵所有黃/藍/（偽）中立嘅市民唱同使用美金？有三個選項：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. Markup 港元價格，美金收正常價<br />\n2. 港元正常價，美金俾 discount<br />\n3. Why not both? 港元 markup, 美金 discount</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家諗下，如果大排檔碟頭飯收 5-6 USD, 但係港幣就要俾 $80，你點揀？ 間間餐廳都咁做嘅話，港幣真係名存實亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得呢個方法可唔可行？<br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<br />\n[推黃色經濟圈+鼓勵唱美金嘅方法？] 接受美元付款！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1718663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1718663</a>"},{"pid":"0f489edf5852bab58d72431ce33b5500fd421774","tid":2046653,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936a0b9dd17ee73868bce7db67a061627e89ed6d","tid":2046653,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8157a3b698970648a8214cc38311ebaa3f6e1ccd","tid":2046653,"uid":21493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-